how to build:

 git submodule init
 git submodule update 
 cd external && ruby build.rb
 cd ../src
 rm -rf build && mkdir build && cd build
 cmake ..  (cmake -G "Visual Studio 9 2008" .. on Windows)
 make  (devenv LZMAService.sln on Windows)

A dir LZMA should be generated which is your service ready to 
be installed using the BrowserPlus SDK:

http://browserplus.yahoo.com/developer/service/sdk/
